                  , in the peace of God and our Lord the King then and there being, feloniously, wilfully, and of their<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178612150003"></xptr>malice aforethought, did make an assault, and that he, the said 
                     <persName id="t17861215-1-person55">
                        Michael
                         Walker
                     <interp inst="t17861215-1-person55" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
